{"tid":2013294,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"被大家忽略的戰場","createTime":"2020-05-12T08:03:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-12T08:09:04.000Z","uid":269108,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b0c186211101e8df88804b10fdf501c5f36fd903","tid":2013294,"uid":269108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T08:03:34.000Z","msg":"【光復法團   從關注屋苑事務做起】<br />\n<br />\n區選過後，大家都將目光放到九月立法會選舉同黃色經濟圈上面，但除此之外，有一個主戰場卻被大家遺忘，就是屋苑法團。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">長期以來，不少法團都是建制人士的地區樁腳，即使現時我們能夠取得區議會的大多數，仍然經常見到法團委員協助落選議員擺街站。要光復香港，避免讓建制再次控制地區工作，請勿忽略法團的影響力。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n在反修例運動之前，我們可能只專注工作，忽略生活中好多細節，例如不會出席法團例會，對於屋苑維修基金有多少，甚至連屋苑更換管理公司都全不知情。<br />\n<br />\n「生活即政治」，關心香港，同樣需要關注屋苑這個小社區。法團委員和議員一樣，都是民選出來，同時需要大家去監察、參與討論、交流意見。<br />\n<br />\n五月十六日是富健花園業主週年大會，當日會投票選出新一屆法團，有一班熱心街坊從331開始，一直投放時間和心血，每日開街站，就是為了喚醒大家去關注自己屋苑更多。富健街坊請預留出席週年大會，運用你手上的一票，自己屋苑自己救。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2963602933760462&amp;id=2333622620091833\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D2963602933760462%26id%3D2333622620091833&d=EvsgW2mpOVZdTd1tTx%2BWmCZO8jd1M6XCUNMtuDfdPZA%3D&h=7202182b\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2963602933760462&amp;id=2333622620091833</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一齊郁法團喇！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"97ae73e817c80382f3b2070967e1a18407c18f65","tid":2013294,"uid":269108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T08:04:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"01a97d834b4f812d41a2a5b226994e4b8e6a76ec","tid":2013294,"uid":269108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T08:04:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 推推"},{"pid":"bbba07a0443e238bd21ad3c1f726cfc776037d74","tid":2013294,"uid":269108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T08:04:59.000Z","msg":"推1"},{"pid":"84f7ca347322a646f4c66ce8ba20928de2992eb1","tid":2013294,"uid":269108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T08:05:59.000Z","msg":"推到俾自己老豆老母睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a32cffd3b2733aa0d1c8b9379408ac89c20637a7","tid":2013294,"uid":269108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T08:06:30.000Z","msg":"推埋俾親戚睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19d12fda0b1ab94124ccbb0f4286b128528f7f16","tid":2013294,"uid":269108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T08:06:48.000Z","msg":"p牌推唔郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27195216e21153d37a9117d84c9539d592082683","tid":2013294,"uid":269108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T08:08:53.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"3890ccee03a5d253afee5916e2a0143155d68786","tid":2013294,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T08:09:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}